Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,

The following reimbursement <%= @expenses.one? ? "claim is" : "claims are" %> charged to a budget you own and <%= @expenses.one? ? "needs" : "need" %> your sign-off before the finance team can pay <%= @expenses.one? ? "it" : "them" %>:

<% @expenses.each do |expense| %>
- #<%= expense.auto_number %> — <%= expense.budget&.name %>
  Payee: <%= expense.effective_payee_name %>
  Amount: <%= number_to_currency(expense.amount, unit: "£") %>
  <%= expense.description %>

<% end %>
Review and endorse on My Budgets: <%= admin_reimbursements_my_budgets_url %>

You're getting this because you own the budget. Any one owner can endorse, and each claim clears as soon as one of you does — you'll get this daily until they're all resolved.

Regards,

Pineapple
